sequenceDiagram
    actor User as User / Analyst
    participant NB as Notebook 05<br/>(Scala)
    participant GPT as Azure OpenAI<br/>GPT-4o
    participant SQL as Spark SQL<br/>(Gold Tables)
    participant NEO as Neo4j<br/>(HTTP API)

    User->>NB: "Find circular transaction patterns"
    NB->>GPT: System prompt + user question
    Note over GPT: Classifies as graph query<br/>Generates bounded Cypher

    GPT-->>NB: JSON response<br/>target: "cypher"<br/>query: "MATCH (a1)-[:T]->(a2)..."

    alt target = "sql"
        NB->>SQL: spark.sql(query)
        SQL-->>NB: DataFrame
    else target = "cypher"
        NB->>NEO: POST /db/neo4j/tx/commit<br/>Cypher query
        NEO-->>NB: JSON results
        Note over NB: Parse JSON → DataFrame
    end

    NB-->>User: Display results table
